      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition car that is about as clean and well-kept as you could hope to find. It runs and drives beautifully, presents extremely well inside and out, and shows only the slightest signs of careful use. A standout example for a buyer who wants a car that feels properly cared for and ready to enjoy right away.",
