    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with straightforward value. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer seeking a budget-friendly option and a practical starting point for daily use, light project plans, or a dependable spare. Offered with transparent positioning and priced to reflect its condition, it presents an accessible opportunity for someone who values low upfront cost and honest potential.",
