      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runaround that still starts up and gets the job done. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but if you\u2019re after affordable wheels, a first car, or a handy project, this one has plenty to offer for the money. Straightforward, budget-friendly, and ideal for someone who wants something practical without spending big. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with a durable powertrain and solid project-driver appeal. Starts up, idles cleanly, and pulls through the rev range with good throttle response. Transmission shifts as it should, steering feels direct, and the chassis is straightforward to sort for someone who knows their way around maintenance. Cosmetically it shows age and wear, but that is reflected in the price. Great candidate for a budget commuter, weekend fixer, or parts-saving enthusiast build.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest poor-condition car with plenty of life for the right buyer. Cheap entry, solid beater, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell. It has that seasoned, road-worn presence that makes it feel approachable, unpretentious, and ready for someone who sees potential where others only see age. Whether you\u2019re after an inexpensive daily driver, a practical backup vehicle, or a hands-on project to make your own, this one offers a lot of opportunity for the right buyer. A budget-friendly entry into ownership with personality to spare.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable opportunity for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it still presents as a straightforward value purchase with plenty of potential at this price point.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants cheap transport, a first project, or a practical runaround. It\u2019s being sold honestly as a used vehicle that shows its age, but it still has value and could make a great little car for someone handy or not afraid of a few cosmetic and mechanical odds and ends. Priced to sell and open to sensible interest.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with a complete drivetrain and plenty of upside for the next owner. It starts, moves, and has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a driver that\u2019s been around, but the core mechanical package feels like a good foundation for a budget build, weekend toy, or restoration candidate. Engine bay appears largely intact, transmission engages, and the chassis presents as a usable platform with character rather than a picked-over parts car. Great opportunity for someone who knows their way around maintenance and wants something affordable with real potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
